better in the studio.

00:30:49.180 --> 00:30:50.582 line:95%,end
I'm not gonna lie, I did.

00:30:50.648 --> 00:30:52.317 line:95%,end
I thought-- but I think
they're always better in the studio.

00:30:52.717 --> 00:30:54.352 line:95%,end
- I don't know.
- [cheering]

00:30:54.419 --> 00:30:56.421 line:95%,end
Good job!

00:30:57.755 --> 00:30:58.957 line:95%,end
You did good.

00:31:01.826 --> 00:31:03.528 line:95%,end
ABBY: What did you think
of Chloe's performance?

00:31:05.830 --> 00:31:09.133 line:95%,end
I thought it was good.
