00:31:09.200 --> 00:31:10.802 line:95%,end
I thought she did it better in the studio.

00:31:12.403 --> 00:31:13.905 line:95%,end
I know Chloe can be great.

00:31:13.972 --> 00:31:15.173 line:95%,end
I've seen her be great.

00:31:15.240 --> 00:31:16.608 line:95%,end
Well, we need to get back to being great.

00:31:16.674 --> 00:31:18.509 line:95%,end
I-- I realize that,
and that's what I said to her.

00:31:18.576 --> 00:31:20.645 line:95%,end
And I'm sorry, Kelly, if this offends you.

00:31:20.712 --> 00:31:27.151 line:95%,end
But Chloe's future can't be at the expense
of your two kids.

00:31:27.218 --> 00:31:29.254 line:95%,end
Melissa, you can tell
all the other moms about it.

00:31:29.320 --> 00:31:30.188 line:95%,end
Right?

00:31:30.255 --> 00:31:31.489 line:95%,end
MELISSA: You know,
sometimes people make mistakes.

00:31:31.556 --> 00:31:32.891 line:95%,end
And you make mistakes, Abby, too.

00:31:32.957 --> 00:31:34.325 line:95%,end
- I've made lots of mistakes.
- OK.

00:31:34.392 --> 00:31:35.226 line:95%,end
So have I.

00:31:35.293 --> 00:31:37.028 line:95%,end
You are more worried
about your friendships

00:31:37.095 --> 00:31:39.397 line:95%,end
with all these women than your own kids,
and you know it.

00:31:39.464 --> 00:31:40.531 line:95%,end
- MELISSA: My kids-- no.
- ABBY: The same thing

00:31:40.698 --> 00:31:41.933 line:95%,end
about worrying about a guy

00:31:42.033 --> 00:31:43.201 line:95%,end
instead of your own kids.

00:31:43.268 --> 00:31:44.535 line:95%,end
Yes.

00:31:44.602 --> 00:31:45.637 line:95%,end
MELISSA: My kids come first to me.

00:31:45.703 --> 00:31:47.338 line:95%,end
