and what looks bad.

00:33:41.519 --> 00:33:43.888 line:95%,end
Straight legs. Straight legs, all of you.

00:33:43.955 --> 00:33:45.423 line:95%,end
100 times better.

00:33:45.490 --> 00:33:46.891 line:95%,end
Yay!

