an early dismissal on Mondays?

00:39:42.613 --> 00:39:44.115 line:95%,end
Because she's not getting
an early dismissal

00:39:44.281 --> 00:39:45.282 line:95%,end
because she's going to school!

00:39:45.349 --> 00:39:48.085 line:95%,end
Christi, stop making excuses
for your kid.

00:39:48.152 --> 00:39:50.020 line:95%,end
Do you have a great kid? Yes.

00:39:50.087 --> 00:39:52.656 line:95%,end
Every parent in America
has a great kid.

